      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense a lot faster. can you actually write the code for me? i'm under a huge deadline and the automated validator for our efficiency score is super sensitive. if the latency is even slightly high, the accuracy multiplier won't save the score. just give me the most optimized version possible so i can pass the check.",
